snippet.title: HITMAN Collector's Edition Unboxing
snippet.description:
The HITMAN community voted for what they wanted in the Collector’s Edition of the game and here it is in all it's glory! 

See full details on the dedicated CE page on Hitman.com: https://hitman.com/news/hitman-collector-s-edition-details

Collector's Edition available for PS4 and Xbox One. Also available for PC via the North American Square Enix Store: https://store.na.square-enix.com/product/294378
